  "mail.hint-crop": "Now that you've got the animals sorted, you might want to think about your crops. They say farmers who've shipped a good number of harvests catch the eye of Pierre's supplier...",
  "mail.hint-forage": "With your farm running so smoothly, maybe it's time to explore the valley more. Seasoned foragers tend to attract attention from the Adventurer's Guild...",
  "mail.hint-tree": "Robin mentioned she's been looking for someone who really knows their way around timber. Put in the work and she might have something special for you.",
  "mail.hint-scavenger": "Gunther at the museum was asking about you. He says dedicated collectors sometimes discover tools that help with their excavations...",
  "mail.hint-machine": "Word around town is that Clint has been working on something big. He says only the most successful farmers earn the privilege of seeing it.",
  "mail.unlock-crop": "Your dedication to farming has paid off! Here's a blueprint for a specialized Crop Grabber that can automatically harvest your crops.",
  "mail.unlock-forage": "Your foraging skills have impressed the valley. Here's a blueprint for a Forage Grabber that can gather wild items for you.",
  "mail.unlock-tree": "Robin was right about you! Here's a blueprint for a Tree Grabber to help you manage your orchards and woodland.",
  "mail.unlock-scavenger": "Gunther is thrilled with your contributions. He found this old blueprint in the museum archives for a Scavenger Grabber.",
  "mail.unlock-machine": "Clint's masterwork is finally ready. Here's the blueprint for his Machine Grabber, the ultimate in automated collection."
}